* Gorgeous two-story with welcoming front porch offering columns, attractive stone detail and concrete foundation/steps for longevity.
* Well maintained hand scraped hardwood flooring throughout foyer, dining room and kitchen. 
* Gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, gas cooktop, vented range hood, double wall ovens, extensive cabinetry, designer tile backsplash, center island offering seating and farmhouse sink seating, granite counters, walk-in pantry, soft close cabinetry,  recessed plus pendant and under cabinet lights.  
* Dinette with abundant natural light and upgraded wheel chandelier.  Gracious open floor plan for entertaining and family time.
* Spacious 2-story living room highlights natural stone gas fireplace with wood mantel. Wall-of-windows offering incredible views.
* Convenient private office with French doors.
* Flex room with closet for bedroom, toy room, exercise room, secondary home office, so many options.
* Mud room off garage features huge walk-in closet, drop station for all your extras, built-in boot bench with coat hooks and shelving for easy storage.
* Attractive full bath with tile tub surround.
Upper Level
* Master suite features impressive recessed ceiling and peaceful views. Double door entry to the master bath offering elegance with luxurious practicality;  tile floor, durable double sink vanity, vanity hutch,  ample cabinetry, large window, private water closet, claw-foot soaking tub and tiled shower. Large walk-in closet.
* 4 bedrooms on one level.  All with generous closet space. One ensuite.
* Full bath with double sink vanity.
* Laundry room offers shelving and folding counter.  Washer and dryer included.
Lower Level
* Walk-out.
* Expansive family room with wall-of-windows and easy access to patio and backyard. 
* Recreation room perfect for gaming; ping-pong, billiards and more?
* Secondary bedroom with so much to offer.
* Stunning full bath.
* 2 Clean storage rooms plus under-step storage.
Additional
* 3 car garage with loads of storage space, finished durable walls, plus concrete driveway.
* Main level 10 foot ceilings. Premium iron balusters and high-profile trim.
* Full yard sprinkler system.
* Quality window coverings throughout.
* Backyard Trex deck and quaint front porch.
All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.

description:

Lower Level

* Exercise room with multiple closets.
* 2 Secondary bedrooms with so many options.
* Impressive 3/4 bath with tile floor, private water closet with shower.

Additional Features
* Built-in sound systems.
* 10? and 12? ceilings throughout.
* Upgraded newer luxurious carpet.
* 3 car extra deep garage is insulated with finished walls, heated and offers epoxy floors. Higher ceilings to accommodate loads of storage. 
* Stamped concrete driveway.
* Attractive stamped concrete covered front porch.
* Main level deck with in-floor lighting.
* Paver patio with propane firepit included.
* Quality association maintained.

description:
Recently sold: $711,251. Main Level
* Gorgeous foyer offers gleaming hand-scraped hardwood floors that flow from foyer to dining room, kitchen, dinette and 1/2 bath.
* Office with elegant French doors, custom built-ins to keep you organized, piano windows for natural light all while maintaining privacy and front yard view.
* Formal dining room with archway entrances and serene mealtime views.
* Living room highlights enameled mantel surround gas fireplace flanked by built-ins and wall-of-windows to let the outdoors in. 
* Kitchen features stainless steel appliances including gas cooktop, double wall ovens, timeless tile backsplash, ample cabinetry, granite countertops, huge center island with adjacent integrated table, walk-in pantry, above the sink window, pendant plus recessed and under cabinet lighting.  Easy deck access.
* Butler pantry with granite countertop, tile backsplash and under cabinet lighting.
* Mud room offers tile floor, walk-in closet, boot bench, storage cubbies with coat hooks and garage foyer.  Enjoy window overlooking sport court.
* Attractive 1/2 bath with pedestal sink.
Upper Level
* Master suite features double door entry, elegant recessed ceiling with fan and peaceful views.  Luxurious master bath offers tile flooring, granite double sink vanity, private water closet, walk-in closet, window, tile surround whirlpool tub and walk-in tile shower stall.  Walk-thru to flex room: exercise room/home office/second closet with window.
* 3 spacious bedrooms on one level. All include ceiling fans.
* Two 3/4 ensuites for each secondary bedroom both with tile floor, pocket door, walk-in shower stall and walk-in closet with window.
* Laundry room offers tile floor, utility sink, cabinets, counterspace and hanging rod. Conveniently located to bedrooms with walk through to master!
Lower Level
* Family room features tile surround gas fireplace flanked by windows with bench seat and recessed lighting. 
* Wet bar offers tile floor, amazing 2-tiered granite countertop with matching backsplash, full refrigerator, sink, wine rack, beverage refrigerator, pendant and recessed lighting.
* Theater room offers sconce lighting, tiered seating, double door entry, projector and screen.
* Sport Court with basketball hoop?so much to offer.
* Secondary bedroom with walk-in closet.
* 3/4 bath with tile floor and tile shower.
Additional Features
* Lifetime warranty Hunter Douglas window treatments.
* Newer LG washer & Dryer.
* Main level deck with steps that lead to the fenced area with heated pool.
* Outdoor heated pool with electronic cover, basketball hoop and diving board. Attractive pool fence leaving partial lot open for recreation.
* Private cul-de-sac lot with mature trees.
All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.

Recently sold: $231,000. Welcome Home! Bright and cheery end unit town home situated on a corner lot with loads of green space. Beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath town home. The thoughtful floor plan creates a sense of spaciousness. Many updates & upgrades throughout including, fresh, neutral paints, carpet, enameled woodwork/ trim, appliances and light fixtures. The kitchen offers ample storage, neutral cabinets, stainless appliances and eat-in counter top. The dining space leads directly to deck to enjoy outdoor dining or grilling and adjoins the vaulted living room. Enjoy more living space in the spacious lower level with 1/2 bath. Desirable location: close to shopping, restaurants, trails, parks and quick access to freeway. Home Sweet Home!

Recently sold: $299,000. IMPECCABLY maintained, single-level living town home in high-demand PLYMOUTH CREEK. 2 main floor bedrooms, including generous master en suite with vaulted ceilings  . 2nd floor loft + 3/4th bath is great flex space and could be easily converted to 3rd bedroom suite. Huge eat-in kitchen with newer appliances, ample counter space and storage. Vaulted great room with fireplace opens to large private patio. Main floor laundry room, attached 2 car garage and ample storage throughout. Truly a gem of a home, in a prime location. Wayzata schools - walk to shops, restaurants.

description:
Recently sold: $289,000. All inquiries call 612-655-5462 or email Jay.shearer3@gmail.com. Will be returned promptly.

Originally built in 2008 by Lennar Homes , this single-owner townhome has been meticulously maintained and taken care of. Part of the prestigious Wayzata school district, with the newly renovated high school two miles west, as well as a brand new elementary school.

  All mechanicals (furnace, air conditioner, water heater and softener) and stainless steel appliances (fridge, dishwasher, microwave, and range/stove) in great shape.

The top floor is where the large master bedroom is located featuring a sitting area, master closet and master bath with his/her sinks.  The top floor also contains two very nice sized spare bedrooms, each with it?s own closet.  A very roomy loft/second living room, second full bathroom and washer/dryer make up the rest of the top floor.

The main floor consists of the kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, center granite island, and laminate wood flooring. Closet, utility, bathroom and attached two car garage are in the hallway leading to/from garage.  The spacious living/dining room gives an open feel for relaxation or hosting guests.  Cable pathway for TV/entertainment center allows for a clean look for all your technology.

Close proximity to major highways: 494, 169, and 694/94.  All within 2-4 miles.  Downtown Maple Grove Arbor Lakes shopping area is a 8 minute drive north with tons of shopping and restaurants and 5 minute drive south is downtown Plymouth.  Quite neighborhood with quick access to a gas station and Walgreens.

Seller to pay buyer's agent fee.

description:
Recently sold: $175,000. Welcome to this Pristine Plymouth Townhome. Nestled in an ideal location, this townhome is equipped with two beds, one bath, and an attached garage. This townhome is updated and is nestled near wooded areas and wetlands. Conveniently located to Camelot Lake, walking trails and just off 494 and Bass Lake Road for an easy commute.

Entering the home you are greeted with a cozy living room with a gas-burning fireplace. Next you approach the kitchen that has a large breakfast bar, and room for a nice sized dining room table. The kitchen is sizable and has plenty of cabinet and counter space.

Upstairs you will find two bedrooms, one being the master. The master bedroom is spacious with large windows to invite in natural light. The second bedroom is also on this level, along with an updated full bathroom with granite countertops and easily accessible for both bedrooms.

The outside of this home has a spacious patio to enjoy your morning coffee, or relax after a long day. The home has an attached garage with guest parking right across the street. The townhome has low monthly dues for professionally man- aged association including snow removal, lawn and exterior maintenance, water/sewer, and sanitation services. And if all of this isn't enough the home is walking distance from everything you need, from coffee at Caribou or dinner at Rusty Taco and Solos Pizza Cafe. This is a townhome you will not want to miss!

The lower level is home to a spacious family room with gas fireplace, built-ins & a wonderful wet-bar + an adjoining amusement space surrounded in windows!  Also, don't miss the well appointed lower level bedrooms (some with walk-in closets), 2 bathrooms, exercise room, and mechanical area with extra storage space.
